modules.description: Handles querying an IP2Proxy database file to retrieve detailed proxy and geolocation information for IPv4 and IPv6 addresses. Works directly with database metadata and IP records, enabling lookups by IP address to return structured data such as country, region, ISP, and proxy status. Useful for applications needing real-time IP analysis, such as fraud detection systems or geolocation-based access control.

Performs high-performance lookups in IP2Proxy binary database files to retrieve geolocation and proxy metadata for IPv4 and IPv6 addresses. Exposes structured data including country, region, city, ISP, and proxy type directly from IP address queries. Designed for fraud prevention, access control, and analytics systems requiring precise IP intelligence.
